data.title: AI parking is coming to the Baton Rouge airport
data.description: Baton Rouge Metropolitan Airport is rolling out new AI-enabled parking technology early December through a partnership with Los Angeles–based Metropolis, marking the first installation of its kind at a Louisiana airport.  The system—going online Dec. 3— will manage roughly 2,000 spaces across BTR’s short-term garage and economy lots, offering checkout-free, drive-in/drive-out access designed to speed […]
data.author: Daily Report Staff
